description:
FACTORY CERTIFIED. LOW MILES. PREMIUM SAFETY. NO DEALER FEES.

Step into style, efficiency, and confidence with this Midnight Pine Metallic 2020 Nissan Rogue SV-a factory-certified SUV engineered for comfort, technology, and outstanding fuel economy. With advanced safety features, a smooth ride, and certification-backed peace of mind, this Rogue delivers everything today's drivers want in a modern crossover.

Smart Technology and Comfort in Every Drive
Stay connected with NissanConnect featuring Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, Bluetooth hands-free calling, touch screen display, steering-wheel-mounted audio controls, and six crisp speakers. Dual zone climate control, heated front bucket seats, a power driver seat, remote keyless entry, and automatic temperature control bring comfort to every mile. Heated mirrors, fully automatic headlights, and auto high-beams add everyday convenience.

Safety That Works For You
This Rogue is equipped with lane keeping technology, lane departure warning, blind spot warning, rear parking sensors, rearview camera, anti-whiplash head restraints, dual front and side airbags, stability control, traction control, and a full suite of advanced safety systems designed to keep you and your passengers protected.

Capability and Efficiency in a Stylish Package
Powered by a refined 2.5L I4 matched with a seamless CVT with Xtronic, this Rogue delivers excellent fuel economy at 26/33 MPG. Four-wheel independent suspension, front and rear anti-roll bars, and confident braking with ABS and four-wheel disc brakes complete the ride. The 17-inch aluminum alloy wheels, roof rails, body-color bumpers, and sporty spoiler give it a sharp, modern look.

Inside you'll find practical features everywhere: cloth seats, leather shift knob, floor mats with cargo protector, rear center armrest, split-folding rear seats, and generous interior space for both passengers and gear. The First Aid Kit and numerous comfort touches make this Rogue adventure-ready and family-friendly.

Clean CARFAX. Priced below KBB Fair Purchase Price.

Ford Blue Certified Confidence
Includes a 139-point inspection, Vehicle History Report, roadside assistance, a 3-month/4,000-mile limited warranty from the certified purchase date, and 11,000 FordPass Rewards Points you can use toward your first maintenance visit.

The Mullinax Advantage
At Mullinax, there are absolutely NO DEALER FEES, saving you hundreds instantly compared to major competitors. Thousands of vehicles. Upfront pricing. No haggle. No hassle.

Financing available for almost all credit situations-good, bad, or none at all. All trades welcome.
Venga y compre con confianza, hablamos su idioma.

description:
Experience the perfect blend of style, efficiency, and technology with the 2024 Kia Soul LX. This dynamic compact SUV is ready to elevate your driving experience and fulfill your everyday needs.

Apple CarPlay
Android Auto
Bluetooth
Factory Warranty
Backup Camera

Plus, the LX Technology Package adds advanced safety features like Blind-Spot Collision-Avoidance Assist, Lane Change Assist, and Rear Cross-Traffic Collision Avoidance Assist, ensuring your peace of mind on the road.

New Tires Installed

Powered by a 2.0L I4 DOHC engine and paired with a CVT transmission, this Kia Soul LX delivers an impressive 29 MPG in the city and 35 MPG on the highway, making it a fuel-efficient and cost-effective choice. The front-wheel-drive configuration provides confident handling and responsive performance, whether you're navigating city streets or exploring the open road.

The sleek gray exterior complements the well-appointed interior, which features a modern infotainment system with AM/FM radio, MP3 playback, and HD Audio. Stay connected with the convenience of Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, and enjoy the added comfort of air conditioning, power windows, and remote keyless entry.

Safety is a top priority in the 2024 Kia Soul LX, with features like dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, and an overhead airbag to protect you and your passengers. The 4-wheel disc brakes with ABS and electronic stability control provide added peace of mind, while the rear-view camera helps you maneuver with confidence.

Designed to meet the needs of the modern driver, the Kia Soul LX offers a versatile and practical solution. With its spacious cabin, ample cargo space, and user-friendly technology, this compact SUV is the perfect companion for your daily commute, weekend adventures, and everything in between.

Versatility is a hallmark of the SRX, thanks to its generous cargo capacity and available third-row seating. The reconfigurable rear cargo area allows you to customize the space to suit your needs, whether you're transporting bulky items or embarking on a family adventure.

Elevate your driving experience with the 2006 Cadillac SRX V6. *2009 HUMMER H3 H3x Sport Utility 4D Black with Ebony Leather Interior*

Looking for a rugged SUV that blends bold styling with real off-road capability? Check out this 2009 HUMMER H3 H3x, finished in classic Black and featuring a luxurious Ebony Leather Interior. Built to stand out and built to last, the H3x delivers presence and performance in equal measure.

This H3x trim comes fully loaded with chrome exterior accents, 18-inch chrome wheels, tubular side steps, and a power sunroof making it one of the most stylish and well-equipped versions of the iconic H3.

Inside, the cabin is both durable and upscale, offering heated leather seats, power front seats, a premium Monsoon sound system, in-dash navigation, and Bluetooth connectivity. Whether you re heading into the city or out into the wild, you ll enjoy every mile in comfort.

Under the hood, the H3x is powered by a 3.7-liter 5-cylinder engine paired with a 4-speed automatic transmission and full-time 4WD with low-range gearing perfect for weekend adventures, snow days, or towing your gear with confidence.

To ensure total transparency, every vehicle at Automania comes with a full *CARFAX report*, *AutoCheck report*, and *NMVTIS (National Motor Vehicle Title Information System)* record so you can buy with confidence. Need added peace of mind? Ask about our *extended warranty* options available at an additional cost.

At Automania, we offer financing solutions for all credit types. Whether you re building credit, repairing it, or have an excellent score, our team will help you find a financing plan that works for you.

Don t miss your chance to own this bold and capable 2009 HUMMER H3 H3x. Stop by Automania today for a test drive and experience the difference for yourself.

*Automania Where every car is a dream, and financing is just a phone call away!*

With its sleek black exterior, this Accord exudes a sophisticated elegance that is sure to turn heads. Under the hood, the powerful 3.5L V6 SOHC i-VTEC 24V engine delivers an exhilarating driving experience, while the 5-speed automatic transmission with overdrive ensures a smooth and efficient ride.

This Accord boasts an impressive array of features that cater to your every need:

Automatic temperature control
Front dual zone A/C
Power driver seat
Remote keyless entry
Steering wheel mounted audio controls
Four wheel independent suspension
Front fog lights
Heated Front Bucket Seats
Leather-Trimmed Seat Trim
Power passenger seat
17 Alloy Wheels

Beyond the impressive list of features, this Accord also offers exceptional fuel efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 19 mpg in the city and 29 mpg on the highway. With its spacious and well-appointed interior, the Accord provides a comfortable and refined driving experience, whether you're commuting or embarking on a road trip.

Meticulously maintained and serviced, this 2009 Honda Accord EX-L 3.5 is a true gem in the pre-owned market. With its low mileage of just 136,302 miles, this Accord has plenty of life left to offer. Backed by Honda's renowned reputation for reliability and quality, you can rest assured that this vehicle will provide you with years of dependable and enjoyable driving.

At our dealership, we take pride in offering our customers the best possible value. This 2009 Honda Accord EX-L 3.5 is priced at just $6,000, making it an exceptional opportunity for those seeking a high-quality, well-equipped, and affordable pre-owned vehicle.

We invite you to come in and experience the Accord for yourself. Our knowledgeable sales team is ready to answer any questions you may have and to help you discover why this Accord is the perfect fit for your lifestyle. Don't miss out on this exceptional opportunity visit us today and drive home in the car of your dreams.

This 2011 Kia Sedona LX in Claret Red with Beige cloth interior comes with a clean CARFAX, two previous owners, and 10 documented service history records. Last owned in California, it has 74647 miles and includes Bluetooth, backup warning system, and front/rear air conditioning.

Key features include:

3.5L V6 engine with 6-speed automatic transmission

Front wheel drive

Bluetooth and Sirius satellite radio with 6-speaker AM/FM/CD/MP3 audio system

Power windows, locks, and mirrors with integrated turn signals

Dual manual sliding doors and roof rails

Front and rear air conditioning with rear controls

Reclining 3rd-row 60/40 split-folding bench seat with fold-in-the-floor capability

2nd-row removable captain's chairs with built-in rollers

Remote keyless entry with panic/alarm function

Cruise control and tilt steering wheel with audio controls

Front/rear side curtain airbags, front seat side airbags, and ESC with traction control

Back-up warning system and tire pressure monitoring system

16" steel wheels with all-season tires

EPA-estimated 18 MPG city / 25 MPG highway

This vehicle has received regular maintenance including oil changes, tire rotations, emissions inspections, and various maintenance checks as documented in the CARFAX. Most recently, in November 2023, it had a full maintenance inspection and tire condition check completed at 67,513 miles.

At Hello Auto, all of our used cars are backed with our suite of Hello Benefits. You also get a personal client advisor that walks you through the process from start to finish. No pushy finance managers trying to sell you products you don't need. We never charge over MSRP and pledge to keep our prices fair and transparent from the beginning. We look forward to saying Hello to you soon!

description:
Discover the 2016 Hyundai Sonata Sport, a sleek and sophisticated sedan that seamlessly blends style, performance, and cutting-edge technology. This meticulously maintained vehicle is ready to elevate your driving experience and exceed your expectations.

Boasting a striking blue exterior, the Sonata Sport commands attention with its bold, sculpted lines and chrome accents. Step inside and you'll be greeted by a spacious, well-appointed cabin that showcases premium features such as:

. Cruise Control
. Push Button Start
. USB/AUX Input
. Sirius XM Radio
. Android Auto
. Apple CarPlay
. Backup Camera
. Bluetooth
. Heated Leather Seats
. Sunroof/Moonroof

The Sonata Sport's impressive list of amenities continues with the Sport Value Edition Package, which includes the Hands-Free Smart Trunk, Proximity Key Entry with Push Button Start, and a Conventional Sunroof, among other desirable upgrades.

Powered by a 2.4L 4-Cylinder DGI DOHC engine and paired with a 6-Speed Automatic Transmission with Shiftronic, this Sonata delivers an exceptional balance of efficiency and performance. With an EPA-estimated 25 city/38 highway MPG, you'll enjoy the freedom to explore without frequent stops at the pump.

Safety is paramount, and the Sonata Sport is equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies. Features like Traction Control, ABS Brakes, Electronic Stability Control, and a Rear View Camera provide peace of mind and confidence behind the wheel.

Whether commuting to the office or embarking on a weekend adventure, the 2016 Hyundai Sonata Sport is a truly versatile and rewarding companion. Experience the difference for yourself by scheduling a test drive at our showroom. We're confident this exceptional sedan will exceed your expectations and leave a lasting impression.

This 2016 Volkswagen e-Golf SE Hatchback is a fun, efficient all-electric hatchback thats perfect for daily commuting and city driving. With 53,509 miles, a smooth 1-speed automatic, and front-wheel drive, it delivers quiet, instant electric torque without stopping for gas. The SE trim adds everyday convenience like automatic climate control, Bluetooth audio, and a backup camera, while the DC Fast Charging Package makes it easy to top up quickly on compatible public chargers. Finished in Night Blue Metallic with a Black interior, its a practical five-door with versatile cargo space and Volkswagens solid German feel on the road.

Key Features & Highlights

All-electric e-Golf SE hatchback no gas, smooth and quiet drive

Electric motor with 1-speed automatic and front-wheel drive

DC Fast Charging Package (Plug-In Electric Fast Charge System) for quicker charging on compatible stations

Lithium-ion traction battery with Brake Actuated Limited Slip Differential

Automatic headlights with daytime running lights and heated power mirrors with integrated turn signals

Aluminum wheels and front/rear performance tires for confident handling

Cloth seating with pass-through rear bench seat and versatile cargo area

Multi-zone automatic climate control and air filtration for year-round comfort

Keyless entry with keyless start, power windows, and power door locks

AM/FM/CD/HD/SiriusXM-ready audio with auxiliary input, MP3 capability, and Bluetooth streaming audio

1 LCD monitor in the front plus trip computer, telematics, and smart device integration

Back-up camera for easier parking and reversing

Comprehensive safety features: traction and stability control, multiple airbags, child safety locks, tire pressure monitor, and side-impact protection

Odometer: 53,509 miles

Vehicle history: 4 previous owners with a minor accident reported; inspected by our service team

Elevate your driving experience with this stunning 2017 Chevrolet Cruze Premier. Boasting a sleek silver exterior and a refined interior, this compact sedan is the perfect blend of style and substance.

Key features include:
. Heated Driver & Front Passenger Seat
. Preferred Equipment Group 1SF
. 6 Speaker Audio System Feature
. Air Conditioning
. Power Driver Seat
. Remote Keyless Entry
. 4-Wheel Disc Brakes
. Dual Front Impact Airbags
. Rear Parking Camera

Powered by a 1.4L 4-Cylinder Turbo engine and paired with a 6-Speed Automatic transmission, this Cruze Premier delivers an impressive 30 city/40 highway MPG, making it both efficient and enjoyable to drive.

Step inside and experience the premium Leather-Appointed Seat Trim, Heated Steering Wheel, and Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control, which create a truly luxurious cabin. The Chevrolet MyLink infotainment system with a 7-inch touchscreen keeps you connected and entertained on the go.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like Traction Control, Electronic Stability Control, and a suite of airbags to give you peace of mind behind the wheel.

This 2017 Chevrolet Cruze Premier is an exceptional value, priced at just $9,903. Don't miss your chance to own this well-equipped and meticulously maintained compact sedan.

Our 2017 Mitsubishi Outlander GT Super AWC in Cool Silver blends versatile utility with advanced features for everyday driving ease. Powered by a 3.0 Liter V6 that offers 224hp paired with a 6 Speed Sportronic Automatic transmission. This All Wheel Drive SUV rewards you with nearly 27mpg on the highway, along with a smooth ride with unparalleled comfort. The svelte styling of our Outlander GT is more than adept at turning heads with its sleek silhouette. Notice the prominent alloy wheels, power remote lift-gate, sunroof, LED headlights, and bold grille!

There's room for seven in the upscale GT interior with pushbutton start, leather seating, heated front seats, full power accessories, dual-zone automatic climate control, a sliding/reclining 60/40 split second row, and a 50/50 split third row. The cabin also includes a Smartphone Link Display Audio system with Android Auto®/Apple CarPlay®, Bluetooth® Hands-Free Link, steering wheel controls, dual USB ports, a CD player, available satellite radio, and an optional Rockford Fosgate premium audio system.

Bask in the smart design of our Mitsubishi Outlander that has received superior safety scores thanks in part to a rearview camera, blind spot monitor, lane change assist, advanced airbags, ABS, a tire pressure monitor, and stability/traction control. Generous in space, amenities, and style, our Outlander is everything you're looking for and more! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Test Drive Towards Ownership!

description:
Introducing the **2019 Ford Fiesta SE**, a certified compact vehicle that impressively merges performance, safety, and innovative technology. This model features a robust 1.6L I-4 DOHC engine, generating an engaging 120 horsepower, complemented by a smooth 5-speed manual transmission, ensuring a fun and responsive driving experience.

Safety is a top priority in the Fiesta SE, prominently showcased by its **Rear Camera** feature. This advanced system enhances your awareness by providing a clear view of obstacles while reversing, making tight maneuvers safer and easier. The **Brake Assist** feature takes safety a step further by intelligently detecting emergency braking situations, applying maximum braking force to help prevent accidents. With these features, you can drive with confidence, knowing youre protected.

Connectivity on the go is effortless thanks to **Selective Internet Access**, allowing you to customize your digital experience for real-time updates on sports, news, and weather, all while minimizing distractions. Long road trips will become a breeze with **Cruise Control with Steering Wheel Mounted Controls**. Set your desired speed, and let the system maintain it, reducing driver fatigue and enhancing fuel efficiency during those extended journeys.

The Fiesta SE is equipped with **Variable Valve Timing** technology, optimizing engine performance at various RPMs, leading to improved fuel efficiency and reduced emissions. This makes it not only a powerful choice but also an environmentally conscious one. For added security, the **Ignition Immobilizer** system ensures that your vehicle can only be started with the correct key, thwarting potential theft.

Music lovers will appreciate the **Wireless Audio Streaming** feature, allowing you to connect your favorite playlists and podcasts directly from your mobile device to the vehicle s sound system, transforming every drive into a personalized audio experience.

In summary, the **2019 Ford Fiesta SE** stands out as an exceptional compact car that seamlessly blends safety, performance, and modern technology. Its innovative features cater to the needs of today s drivers, ensuring a comfortable, secure, and enjoyable ride. Don t miss the opportunity to own this remarkable vehicle, which embodies both practicality and style while delivering reliability and efficiency in your daily commutes or weekend adventures.

With Ford s Blue Certified program, you can also benefit from a comprehensive warranty and roadside assistance, adding even more value to your purchase. Experience the perfect balance of functionality and fun with the **2019 Ford Fiesta SE**!

description:
Meet the 2019 Hyundai Elantra SEL a sleek, smart sedan that delivers big value with modern design and everyday comfort. Dressed in Lakeside Blue, this Elantra stands out with its crisp lines, bold front fascia, and aerodynamic profile that still turns heads years later.

Inside, you'll find a surprisingly refined cabin packed with thoughtful tech and convenience features. The SEL trim adds key upgrades like Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, a 7-inch touchscreen display, blind-spot monitoring, and heated side mirrors all designed to make your daily drive more connected and confident.

Under the hood, a 2.0L 4-cylinder engine pairs with a 6-speed automatic transmission with Shiftronic, delivering smooth, efficient performance with up to 37 MPG on the highway. Whether you're commuting through Cache Valley or cruising to Salt Lake, the Elantra makes every mile feel easy.

Stylish, efficient, and packed with features that punch above its class this Elantra SEL is a smart choice for drivers who want more than just basic transportation.

description:
This 2019 Nissan Sentra S is an exceptional value that offers a well-equipped and reliable driving experience. With its sleek gray exterior and spacious interior, this Sentra is the perfect blend of style and practicality.

Carpeted Floor Mats w/Trunk Mat

The Sentra S is packed with features that enhance your driving enjoyment, including:

4 Speakers
AM/FM radio
Radio data system
Radio: AM/FM/Aux-In Audio System
Air Conditioning
Rear window defroster
Power steering
Power windows
Remote keyless entry
Steering wheel mounted audio controls
Speed-sensing steering
Traction control

This Sentra has been meticulously inspected and certified, giving you the peace of mind that comes with a high-quality, well-maintained vehicle. With its impressive fuel efficiency of 27 city/35 highway MPG, the Sentra S delivers exceptional value and cost savings at the pump.

Beneath the hood, you'll find a 1.8L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V engine paired with a CVT with Xtronic transmission, providing a smooth and responsive driving experience. The front-wheel-drive configuration ensures confident handling in a variety of road conditions.

Safety is a top priority, and the Sentra S is equipped with a suite of advanced safety features, including ABS brakes, dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, and electronic stability control. You can drive with confidence, knowing that you and your passengers are protected.

This 2019 Nissan Sentra S is an exceptional value that offers a well-equipped, reliable, and efficient driving experience. With its impressive features and certified status, it's the perfect choice for the discerning buyer. Visit our showroom today to experience the Sentra S for yourself and discover why it's the smart choice for your next vehicle.
